data.description: Welcome to the epitome of luxury living in the highly coveted Sienna Estates neighborhood! This meticulously remodeled 4-bedroom, flex-room can be a 5th bedroom if needed, residence stands as one of the largest homes in the area. The heart of this home lies in its well-appointed kitchen, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, exquisite countertops, and custom cabinetry. Indulge in the ultimate pampering experience in the primary bathroom, complete with a tankless designated water heater ensuring endless hot water supply. The deluxe shower transforms your daily routine into a spa-like retreat. Explore the vibrant community that surrounds it. Enjoy the convenience of being within walking distance to the community pool and amenities. For outdoor enthusiasts, a fishable lake awaits your leisurely afternoons, providing the perfect backdrop for tranquil moments. You will appreciate the proximity to the kids' park and splashpad.
